{"tid":1918301,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"前排返左新公司 我上左個師姐","createTime":"2020-03-10T04:06:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T03:40:23.000Z","uid":230197,"like":3,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a22c97cfa3da44ad5432f82cf4c1f495b6994bbe","tid":1918301,"uid":230197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T04:06:12.000Z","msg":"前排我返左新公司 <br />\n乜都唔識 <br />\n我機緣巧合識左個師姐 <br />\n<br />\n咁有一日佢OT <br />\n我新仔扮勤力 <br />\n同佢OT <br />\n<br />\n公司有張梳化 <br />\n我就訓左係梳化<br />\n我message同佢講我訓係梳化好舒服<br />\n佢就話我依家過黎 <br />\n<br />\n咁佢黎到 我同佢講 <br />\n一齊訓係到 舒服d <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟住2丁友 訓係到 <br />\n跟住隻手摸下佢隻手 <br />\n<br />\n見唔反抗 順便熄燈<br />\n又錫又攬 <br />\n跟住就順便扑埋<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇人有呢d經歷 <br />\n辦公室扑野 後果係點"},{"pid":"8271ddfd079d4365a97b993594918ad6806bbe2e","tid":1918301,"uid":38904,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T04:10:52.000Z","msg":"清潔返對方啲精"},{"pid":"79d4ec417ffc24448351c3f20ad62b0149e37912","tid":1918301,"uid":230197,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"8271ddfd079d4365a97b993594918ad6806bbe2e","tid":1918301,"uid":38904,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T04:10:52.000Z","msg":"清潔返對方啲精"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T04:18:27.000Z","msg":"對方係女"},{"pid":"db1825b3da4cc901f399675747cc3f5b29e7d77b","tid":1918301,"uid":230197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T04:18:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"